extendedInfo.description: Fastest, easiest, lightest and most reliable network booster / signal refresh app in Google Play Store! :)Tired of having a low signal and slow data connection?  Here's the solution to your problem! :)Using the latest Android API technology to renew your phone's connection to the best cell tower available!  What you got to lose, it's free! :)  Download now!The fastest, safest, the most light weight network signal speed booster!

reviews.title: Great app. Love it
reviews.comment: This app works great for me. It always increases signal strength. We live in a mountainous area with very poor reception and at our house we usually have one or two bars. With this app we can continuously get three and sometimes four bars.
